<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>SOPR Emergency Knowledge Hub</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #07111f;
      --bg-deep: #030916;
      --panel: #102238;
      --panel-2: #16304d;
      --text: #edf4fb;
      --muted: #9bb0c7;
      --accent: #7bb7ff;
      --accent-soft: rgba(123, 183, 255, 0.18);
      --border: rgba(158, 190, 227, 0.22);
      --shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(1000px 540px at 50% -5%, rgba(76, 123, 181, 0.28), transparent 62%),
        radial-gradient(900px 400px at 100% 0%, rgba(47, 84, 138, 0.18), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #091426 0%, var(--bg) 46%, var(--bg-deep) 100%);
      font-family: "Segoe UI", "Noto Sans", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.45;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 26px 16px 72px;
    }

    .shell {
      max-width: 1220px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .masthead {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 12px 26px;
    }

    .badge {
      width: 86px;
      height: 86px;
      margin: 0 auto 14px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)),
        var(--panel);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      color: #c8ddff;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .kicker {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 8px 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4vw, 3.35rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
    }

    .intro {
      width: min(760px, 100%);
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .rule {
      height: 1px;
      margin: 18px auto 0;
      width: min(980px, 100%);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent);
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .tile {
      min-height: 186px;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26, 54, 86, 0.96), rgba(14, 31, 51, 0.98));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .tile-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border: 1px solid rgba(174, 207, 241, 0.16);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: #c8ddff;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .tile h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      line-height: 1.12;
    }

    .tile p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .status {
      margin-top: 18px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .metric {
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015)),
        rgba(6, 16, 29, 0.5);
    }

    .metric strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 160px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border: 1px solid #e4efff;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(98, 126, 165, 0.96), rgba(38, 57, 84, 0.98));
      border-top-color: rgba(249, 252, 255, 0.98);
      border-left-color: rgba(236, 244, 255, 0.98);
      border-right-color: rgba(18, 29, 46, 0.96);
      border-bottom-color: rgba(7, 14, 24, 0.98);
      box-shadow:
        inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.34),
        inset -1px -2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42),
        0 8px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      font: inherit;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button:hover {
      box-shadow:
        inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.38),
        inset -1px -2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.46),
        0 10px 22px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
    }

    .button:active {
      transform: translateY(2px);
      border-top-color: rgba(18, 29, 46, 0.96);
      border-left-color: rgba(10, 18, 29, 0.96);
      border-right-color: rgba(248, 252, 255, 0.98);
      border-bottom-color: rgba(236, 244, 255, 0.98);
      box-shadow:
        inset -1px -1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16),
        inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.58),
        0 3px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .grid,
      .status {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .grid,
      .status {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shell">
    <header class="masthead">
      <div class="badge">PM</div>
      <p class="kicker">Offline Emergency Reference System</p>
      <h1>Command Center</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Quick local access to critical survival, medical, maps, and system tools when the internet is unavailable.
      </p>
      <div class="rule"></div>
    </header>

    <main class="grid">
      <section class="tile">
        <div class="tile-icon">⌂</div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Quick Access</span>
        <h2>Kiwix Full Library</h2>
        <p>Browse the offline reference collection for medicine, survival, education, and general knowledge.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="tile">
        <div class="tile-icon">⌖</div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Navigation</span>
        <h2>Offline Maps</h2>
        <p>Open maps and navigation tools prepared for disconnected use in the field or at home.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="tile">
        <div class="tile-icon">⚙</div>
        <span class="eyebrow">System Tools</span>
        <h2>Admin Portal</h2>
        <p>Manage services, review system health, and maintain the device through the local admin area.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="tile">
        <div class="tile-icon">✚</div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Critical</span>
        <h2>Medical & First Aid</h2>
        <p>Fast access to treatment guides, field medicine references, and core emergency health information.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="tile">
        <div class="tile-icon">⛺</div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Sustainment</span>
        <h2>Preparedness & Repair</h2>
        <p>Water, food, sanitation, shelter, mechanical repair, and other practical sustainment topics.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="tile">
        <div class="tile-icon">⟡</div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Rebuild</span>
        <h2>Education & Skills</h2>
        <p>Learning resources for rebuilding capability, teaching others, and extending the knowledge base offline.</p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <section class="status">
      <div class="metric">
        <strong>Disk Status</strong>
        <span>Used / free capacity placeholder</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <strong>System Temperature</strong>
        <span>Raspberry Pi thermal status placeholder</span>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <strong>Services</strong>
        <span>Kiwix, maps, and admin health placeholder</span>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
